snippet.title: Johnny Depp loses libel case over The Sun ‘wife beater’ claim
snippet.description:
A warning: This report contains some upsetting details. (Subscribe: https://bit.ly/C4_News_Subscribe) 

Over three weeks this summer, lurid details of the debauched lifestyle of the Hollywood actor Johnny Depp were revealed in a libel action at London's High Court. 

Mr Depp had gone to court after the Sun newspaper accused him of assaulting his ex-wife Amber Heard. 

Today the Judge said the Sun story was “substantially true”. 

Mr Depp's lawyers called the decision “bewildering”.
